50|$|On November 22, 2008, {{following}} {{the box office}} success of Twilight, Summit Entertainment confirmed a sequel, called <b>The</b> Twilight Saga: <b>New</b> <b>Moon,</b> based on <b>the</b> second book in <b>the</b> series, <b>New</b> <b>Moon.</b> <b>The</b> film was released on November 20, 2009. <b>The</b> Twilight Saga: <b>New</b> <b>Moon</b> was released on DVD and Blu-ray on March 20, 2010 through midnight release parties. That same day, Summit Entertainment released Twilight in Forks, a documentary about the primary setting of the Twilight series, Forks, Washington. Topics Entertainment released its own documentary about Forks and the Twilight series on March 16, called Forks: Bitten by Twilight.|$|R
